# Kaspersky App for Splunk

## System requirements
- Kaspersky Security Center 8 or newer 
- Splunk 7.0 or newer
- Kaspersky Add-on for Splunk

## Installation
Install the app on: 
Search Heads - The app contains dashboards and reports


## Configuration
### Splunk
- Edit the macro `kaspersky_index` and replace index=epav with the index where you kaspersky events are stored.

## Troubleshooting


## Support
You can file bug reports on our [GitHub issue tracker](https://github.com/diogofgm/kaspersky_app/issues) and they will be addressed as soon as possible.
**Support is a volunteer effort** and there is no guaranteed response time.


